ecause wafers can be polluted by gas or particles. But if wafer can move to another space without pollution, process productivity will increase. So, our team developed this equipment prototype to prove our theory.","client":"KITECH","date":"2021","categories":["Industrial"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/39081e5b244d624b5d4077f3e0b51992/d96dd/212.png","srcSet":"/static/39081e5b244d624b5d4077f3e0b51992/4222d/212.png 360w,\n/static/39081e5b244d624b5d4077f3e0b51992/26da8/212.png 720w,\n/static/39081e5b244d624b5d4077f3e0b51992/d96dd/212.png 1440w","srcWebp":"/static/39081e5b244d624b5d4077f3e0b51992/d2002/212.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/39081e5b244d624b5d4077f3e0b51992/7fc23/212.webp 360w,\n/static/39081e5b244d624b5d4077f3e0b51992/5e637/212.webp 720w,\n/static/39081e5b244d624b5d4077f3e0b51992/d2002/212.webp 1440w","sizes":"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px"}}}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/ALD/","next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Bokkda"}},"previous":null}}